quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20uses%20about%200.000085%20gallons%20of%20water%3B%20roughly%20one-fifteenth%20of%20a%20teaspoon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20wrote%20that%20he%20expects%20energy%20to%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20wildly%20abundant%26quot%3B%20in%20the%202030s.%20Energy%2C%20along%20with%20the%20limitations%20of%20human%20intelligence%2C%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20limiters%20on%20human%20progress%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20data%20center%20production%20gets%20automated%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20intelligence%20should%20eventually%20converge%20to%20near%20the%20cost%20of%20electricity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Altman%20has%20predicted%20that%20AI%20will%20become%20cheaper%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Altman%20wrote%20on%20his%20blog%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-cost-using-ai-drop-10-times-every-year-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20using%20AI%20will%20drop%20by%2010%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20this%20in%20the%20token%20cost%20from%20GPT-4%20in%20early%202023%20to%20GPT-4o%20in%20mid-2024%2C%20where%20the%20price%20per%20token%20dropped%20about%20150x%20in%20that%20time%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoore's%20law%20changed%20the%20world%20at%202x%20every%2018%20months%3B%20this%20is%20unbelievably%20stronger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20hoping%20to%20dominate%20in%20AI%20have%20been%20considering%20using%20nuclear%20energy%20to%20power%20their%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-plan-double-triple-data-center-capacity-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20a%2020-year%20deal%20with%20Constellation%20Energy%20to%20reactivate%20one%20of%20the%20dormant%20nuclear%20plants%20located%20in%20Three%20Mile%20Island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-considering-nuclear-power-energy-hungry-ai-data-centers-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-nuclear-power-ai-data-centers-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estruck%20a%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Kairos%20Power%2C%20a%20nuclear%20energy%20company%2C%20to%20make%20three%20small%20modular%20nuclear%20reactors.%20The%20reactors%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20up%20to%20500%20megawatts%20of%20electricity%2C%20are%20set%20to%20be%20ready%20by%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20CEO%2C%20Sundar%20Pichai%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Nikkei%20Asia%20published%20in%20October%20that%20the%20search%20giant%20wants%20to%20achieve%20net-zero%20emissions%20across%20its%20operations%20by%202030.%20He%20added%20that%20besides%20looking%20at%20nuclear%20energy%2C%20Google%20was%20considering%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20ambitious%20target%2C%20and%20we%20are%20still%20going%20to%20be%20working%20very%20ambitiously%20towards%20it.%20Obviously%2C%20the%20trajectory%20of%20AI%20investments%20has%20added%20to%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20task%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-energy-does-chatgpt-use-average-query-watts-altman-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749620435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848fe0d3d5881a51c1b2ab5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b