0latest%20buyout%20offers%20mean%20more%20layoffs%20are%20coming.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-voluntary-exit-pixel-android-group-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20offered%20buyouts%20for%20staff%20in%20its%20Pixel%20and%20Android%20unit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20had%20layoffs%20in%20that%20same%20division%20a%20few%20weeks%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20full%20memo%20sent%20to%20Google%20employees%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20Jen%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20the%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20of%20Core%20Systems%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EHi%20everyone%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20I%20mentioned%20at%20The%20Source%20last%20month%2C%20there's%20a%20ton%20of%20exciting%20and%20important%20work%20for%20us%20here%20in%20Core%2C%20especially%20as%20AI%20is%20reshaping%20everything%20-%20our%20products%2C%20our%20tools%2C%20the%20way%20we%20work%2C%20how%20we%20work%2C%20how%20we%20innovate%20and%20so%20on.%20To%20meet%20this%20transformational%20moment%2C%20we%20need%20everyone%20to%20show%20up%20with%20an%20unparalleled%20sense%20of%20energy%20and%20enthusiasm%20for%20Core's%20mission%2C%20connecting%20and%20collaborating%20at%20speed%20so%20that%20we%20can%20tackle%20all%20of%20the%20ambitious%20work%20we%20need%20to%20do.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20support%20of%20these%20goals%2C%20we're%20introducing%20two%20programs%20today%20for%20US-based%20Core%20Googlers%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe're%20offering%20a%20Voluntary%20Exit%20Program%20(VEP)%20for%20Core%20Googlers%20in%20the%20US%20(in%20my%20reporting%20org).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20We've%20seen%20positive%20feedback%20across%20the%20company%20in%20other%20orgs%20who%20have%20offered%20similar%20programs%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20extend%20the%20same%20option%20to%20eligible%20Core%20Googlers%20in%20the%20US%20who%20would%20like%20to%20leave%20the%20company%20voluntarily%20with%20severance.%20The%20Voluntary%20Exit%20Program%20may%20be%20a%20fit%20Core%20Googlers%20who%20aren't%20feeling%20excited%20about%20and%20aligned%20with%20Core's%20mission%20and%20goals%2C%20or%20those%20who%20are%20having%20difficulty%20meeting%20the%20demands%20of%20their%20role.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EAdditionally%2C%20how%20we%20work%20today%20is%20more%20flexible%20than%20it's%20ever%20been%20with%20our%203%2F2%20hybrid%20work%20policy.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20connection%2C%20collaboration%2C%20and%20moving%20quickly%20to%20innovate%20together%2C%20there's%20just%20no%20substitute%20for%20coming%20together%20in%20person.%20In%20Core%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20having%20more%20Googlers%20in%20the%20office%20collaborating%20and%20innovating%20together%20while%20building%20community%20and%20connection%20that%20supports%20our%20culture%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20our%20success%20as%20an%20org%2C%20and%20as%20a%20company.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThat's%20why%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ewe're%20updating%20our%20work%20location%20policy%20for%20local%20remote%20Core%20Googlers%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20asking%20all%20US-based%20Core%20Googlers%20who%20are%20remote%20and%20live%20within%2050%20miles%20of%20an%20approved%20return%20site%20(%26quot%3Blocal%20remote%26quot%3B)%20for%20Core%20to%20transfer%20back%20to%20a%20return%20site%20on%20a%203%2F2%20hybrid%20schedule.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20ensure%20Core%20Googlers%20are%20fully%20committed%20to%20being%20here%20and%20actively%20contributing.%20These%20programs%20will%20help%20us%20be%20even%20more%20focused%20on%20our%20mission%20and%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20operate%20with%20greater%20velocity%2C%20efficiency%20and%20collaboration.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20isn't%20about%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20pe