20media%20marketing%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20overseeing%20Hooters'%20bankruptcy%20would%20need%20to%20approve%20the%20bid%2C%20and%20its%20terms%20could%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20bid%20puts%20Hulk's%20company%20in%20direct%20competition%20with%20a%20proposal%20led%20by%20Hooters%20Inc.%2C%20which%20oversees%20some%20franchised%20Hooters%20locations%20and%20is%20run%20by%20CEO%20Neil%20Kiefer%2C%20one%20of%20Hooters'%20original%20cofounders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20successful%2C%20the%20Real%20American-led%20bid%20would%20aim%20to%20grow%20the%20Hooters%20business%2C%20including%20through%20new%20revenue%20streams%20like%20merchandise%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20bid%20told%20BI.%20The%20person%20was%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20publicly%20about%20the%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20find%20a%20strategy%20that%20could%20get%20more%20diners%2C%20especially%20people%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s%2C%20stopping%20by%20Hooters'%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCheap%20beer%20and%20fattening%20wings%20aren't%20the%20food%20or%20drink%20of%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said.%20%26quot%3BHulk%20can%20solve%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223006e6ce-7a22-4319-9013-0fb41d0fcb29%5C%22%3EHooters'%20debt%20could%20be%20key%20to%20Hulk's%20bid%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Real%20American%20bid%20faces%20some%20challenges.%20For%20one%2C%20Real%20American%20would%20have%20to%20find%20another%20entity%20to%20own%20the%20Hooters%20locations%20since%20US%20liquor%20laws%20prevent%20alcohol%20brands%20from%20owning%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20is%20satisfying%20Hooters%20of%20America%20bondholders%2C%20the%20person%20familiar%20with%20Real%20American's%20bid%20said.%20Under%20current%20plans%2C%20Hooters%20of%20America%20would%20continue%20paying%20bondholders%20what%20they're%20owed%2C%20according%20to%20bankruptcy%20filings.%20The%20company