ery%20comfortable%20due%20to%20memory%20foam%20insoles%2C%20and%20can%20be%20worn%20with%20or%20without%20socks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Budget%20Dress%20Shoe%3A%20Florsheim%20Midtown%20Cap%20Toe%20Oxford%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Florsheim%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68484cb5f748d8c055f3622b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Amelinckx%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFlorsheim's%20Midtown%20cap%20toe%20Oxfords%20nicely%20balance%20price%20with%20quality%20that%2C%20like%20all%20the%20footwear%20I've%20tried%20from%20the%20brand%2C%20hold%20up%20well%2C%20with%20the%20bonus%20that%20they're%20really%20comfortable%20for%20all-day%20wear%20and%20are%20available%20at%20Famous%20Footwear.%20For%20%24125%20you%20get%20a%20great%20looking%20dress%20shoe%20made%20from%20leather%20sourced%20from%20environmentally%20responsible%20tanneries%20with%20Goodyear%20welted%20construction%20(meaning%20it%20can%20be%20resoled)%2C%20plus%20tons%20of%20cushioning%2C%20and%20they'll%20hold%20up%20well%20for%20years%20if%20properly%20cared%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Luxury%3A%20Allen%20Edmonds%20Park%20Avenue%20Oxford%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Allen%20Edmonds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684856033d5881a51c1b1c51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Amelinckx%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20iconic%20gets%20thrown%20around%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20in%20the%20case%20of%20American%20heritage%20brand%20Allen%20Edmonds%20and%20its%20Park%20Avenue%20cap%20toe%20Oxford%2C%20it's%20an%20apt%20description%20and%20while%20they're%20considered%20luxury%2C%20the%20craftsmanship%20and%20top-notch%20materials%20justify%20the%20cost.%20They%20handcraft%20these%20timeless%20dress%20shoes%20in%20Wisconsin%20using%20212%20steps%2C%20European%20calfskin%2C%20Goodyear%20welting%2C%20and%20cork%20insoles%20that%20mold%20to%20the%20shape%20of%20your%20foot%20over%20time%2C%20making%20for%20a%20refined%20pair%20of%20Oxfords%20that%20deliver%20a%20comfortable%20wearing%20experience%2C%20will%20last%20decades%2C%20and%20can%20be%20recrafted%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Dress%20Boot%3A%20Idrese%20Galahad%20Jodhpur%20boots%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Idrese%20Jaohdpur%20boots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68471b2185e81483682bb710%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221131%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Amelinckx%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIdrese%20is%20a%20direct-to-consumer%20shoe%20company%20that%20handcrafts%20its%20footwear%20in%20Spain%2C%20and%20while%20it%20specializes%20in%20letting%20the%20customer%20design%20their%20own%20shoes%20and%20boots%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20what%20I%20did%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20Jodhpurs%20that%20I%20absolutely%20love%20and%20fit%20my%20feet%20perfectly%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20also%20has%20ready%20to%20wear%20items%20like%20the%20Galahad%20jodhpurs.%20Idrese%20uses%20supple%20Italian%20calfskin%20leather%2C%20Goodyear%20welting%2C%20and%20a%20sleek%20profile%20for%20an%20elevated%20take%20on%20this%20boot%20style%20that%20includes%20a%20strap%20and%20buckle%20near%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Derby%3A%20Moral%20Code%20Chase%20Derby%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moral%20Code%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68485f6385e81483682bcba5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKara%20Thurmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Derby%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20Oxford%2C%20has%20open%20lacing%20and%20is%20less%20formal%20than%20its%20cousin%2C%20and%20Moral%20Code's%20version%20plays%20this%20up%20with%20its%20thick%20EVA%20soles%2C%20but%20still%20gives%20your%20outfits%20polish.%20I've%20had%20a%20pair%20of%20these%20for%20three%20years%20and%20they%20still%20look%20new%2C%20are%20incredibly%20comfortable%20for%20all%20day%20wear%2C%20and%20pair%20equally%20well%20with%20jeans%20as%20they%20do%20with%20a%20sport%20coat%20and%20chinos%20or%20even%20a%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Monk%20Strap%3A%20Thursday%20Boots%20the%20Saint%20Double%20Monk%20Strap%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222789%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thursday%20Boots%20Saint%20Monk%20Strap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684719c93d5881a51c1b08f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKara%20Thurmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20rich%20history%20dating%20back%20centuries%20to%20their%20modern%20appeal%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20less%20fashion-forward%20Oxfords%2C%20monk%20strap%20dress%20shoes%20%E2%80%94%20with%20their%20unique%20straps%20and%20buckles%20(one%20or%20two)%20rather%20than%20laces%20%E2%80%94%20look%20as%20good%20with%20a%20contemporary%20suit%20as%20they%20do%20with%20nice%20jeans%2C%20so%20they%20won't%20get%20dusty%20waiting%20for%20formal%20occasions%20to%20be%20worn.%20The%20DTC%20footwear%20brand%20Thursday%20Boots%20makes%20the%20Saint%20double-monk%20strap%20from%20sleek%20full-grain%20leather%20using%20Blake%20stitching%2C%20with%20straps%20that%20are%20sturdy%2C%20stay%20in%20place%2C%20and%20have%20a%20good%20range%20of%20adjustability%20for%20a%20tighter%20or%20looser%20fit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20with%20a%20minimal%20break-in%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20consider%20when%20shopping%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20important%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20looking%20for%20dress%20shoes%20that%20will%20last%20you%20years.%20The%20shoes%20should%20be%20made%20of%20high-quality%20leather%20rather%20than%20a%20synthetic%20material%20(unless%20you're%20morally%20opposed%20to%20it).%20The%20shoes%20should%20have%20either%20Goodyear%20welting%20or%20Blake%20stitching%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20cemented%2C%20as%20you%20see%20with%20sneaker%20construction.%20These%20two%20old-school%20techniques%20for%20attaching%20the%20upper%20to%20the%20sole%2C%20allow%20you%20to%20have%20them%20resoled%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20Oxfords%20and%20Derbies%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOxford%20have%20closed%20lacing%2C%20meaning%20the%20part%20of%20the%20shoe%20called%20the%20quarters%2C%20where%20the%20laces%20go%2C%20are%20sewn%20under%20the%20vamp%20(front%20part%20of%20the%20shoe)%20making%20for%20a%20sleeker%20shoe%20that's%20considered%20more%20formal%20than%20Derbies.%20The%20latter%20type%20of%20shoe%20has%20open%20lacing%2C%20meaning%20the%20quarters%20are%20sewn%20over%20the%20vamp%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20shoes%20a%20more%20relaxed%20look%20and%20allows%20for%20greater%20ease%20of%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20care%20for%20leather%20dress%20shoes%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20simple%20steps%20to%20keeping%20your%20dress%20shoes%20looking%20sharp.%20Depending%20on%20how%20often%20you%20wear%20them%2C%20you%20should%20shine%20them%20every%20few%20weeks%20if%20they%20get%20heavy%20use%20or%20every%20few%20months%20if%20you%20don't%20wear%20them%20as%20often.%20First%2C%20clean%20them%20with%20saddle%20soap%2C%20then%20use%20a%20moisturizing%20cream%20polish%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20high%20shine%2C%20use%20a%20wax%20polish.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-shoe-polish%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20the%20six%20you%20should%20use%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20dress%2