%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-viewers-fuel-youtube-tv-growth-nielsen-data-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20blown%20past%20prestige%20streamers%20like%20Netflix%20and%20Disney%2B%20to%20become%20the%20biggest%20TV%20company%20by%20viewership.%20And%20the%20traditional%20media%20business%20is%20about%20to%20get%20another%20wake-up%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20ad%20revenue%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcreator-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreator-driven%3C%2Fa%3E%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20LinkedIn%20will%20exceed%20ad%20revenue%20driven%20by%20studios%20and%20media%20companies%20known%20for%20their%20professionally%20made%20content%2C%20WPP%20Media's%20new%20mid-year%20global%20ad%20forecast%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20Media%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20part%20of%20ad%20holding%20company%20giant%20WPP%20%E2%80%94%20estimated%20that%20the%20ad%20revenue%20generated%20by%20those%20creator-driven%20platforms%20would%20just%20exceed%20the%20%24235%20billion%20driven%20by%20TV%2C%20audio%2C%20print%2C%20and%20cinema%20companies%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20shift%20from%202019%2C%20when%20WPP%20estimated%20that%20professional%20content%20companies'%20share%20of%20content-based%20ad%20revenue%20topped%2070%25%2C%20with%20creator-driven%20platforms%20driving%20the%20rest%2C%20said%20Kate%20Scott-Dawkins%2C%20global%20president%20of%20Business%20Intelligence%20at%20WPP%20Media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20definition%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-tiktok-mrbeast-creator-economy-next-year-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreator%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20blurry.%20It%20adjusted%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20some%20of%20the%20revenue%20generated%20by%20those%20creator-driven%20platforms%20comes%20from%20professional%20sources%2C%20as%20when%20companies%20like%20Disney%20and%20Comcast%20put%20clips%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20also%20categorized%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20YouTubers%2C%20like%20MrBeast%2C%20who's%20made%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-prime-renews-mrbeasts-beast-games-for-more-seasons-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejump%20to%20Amazon's%20Prime%20Video%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20competition%20show%2C%20as%20professional%20content%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20WPP's%20estimate%20includes%20TikTok%2C%20it%20excludes%20China-based%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20separately%20calculated%20the%20revenue%20going%20to%20creators%20directly.%20The%20firm%20estimated%20revenue%20would%20total%20about%20%24185%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20up%2020%25%20from%202024%2C%20and%20double%20to%20more%20than%20%24376%20billion%20by%202030.%20WPP%20estimated%20that%20about%2060%25%20of%20that%20revenue%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20brands%20and%20sponsorship%20deals%2C%20with%20the%20remainder%20from%20other%20sources%2C%20including%20the%20revenue%20split%20that%20platforms%20like%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-is-trying-to-ahead-of-netflix-advertising-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0share%20with%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20said%20that%20sources%20of%20revenue%20for%20traditional%20media%20are%20largely%20declining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETV%20advertising%20is%20slated%20to%20grow%20just%201%25%20this%20year%2C%20to%20%24162.5%20billion.%20A%20quarter%20of%20that%20comes%20from%20streaming%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20rapidly%2C%20by%2012.5%25%20in%202025%20and%20to%20about%20%2472%20billion%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAudio%20(which%20includes%20video%20advertising%20formats%20attached%20to%20podcasts)%20will%20be%20flat%20at%20%2426.5%20billion%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrint%20will%20continue%20its%2