wers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20month%2C%20I%20had%20one%20lakh%20subscribers.%20Views%20were%20in%20millions.%20Our%2010-day%20revenue%20was%20above%20Rs%201%2C00%2C000.%20What%20we%20did%20not%20earn%20in%20two%20years%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20earn%20in%20one%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20reminder%20that%20our%20language%20and%20culture%20resonated%20with%20people%20and%20have%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20not%20only%20shared%20recipes%2C%20but%20also%20proverbs%20and%20traditional%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20things%20people%20were%20slowly%20forgetting.%20%E2%80%9CA%20Rajasthani%20living%20in%20the%20US%20messaged%20me%20saying%20watching%20the%20video%20made%20him%20feel%20like%20he%20was%20back%20home.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20knew%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20my%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20viral%20videos%20to%20MasterChef%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20an%20unexpected%20call%20from%20MasterChef%20India%20changed%20her%20life%20once%20again.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20prank.%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20my%20husband%20to%20answer%20the%20call%20because%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20why%20someone%20from%20Sony%20TV%20would%20like%20to%20talk%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-09T192407.344-1749477265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kaushalya%20on%20Masterchef%20India%202024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-09T192407.344-1749477265.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe