20units.%20I%20knew%20immediately%20that%20this%20was%20where%20I%20wanted%20to%20begin%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20lightbulb%20moment%20for%20Krithika.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20trying%20to%20incorporate%20all%20his%20techniques%20in%20my%20project.%20I%20was%20studying%20and%20researching%20more.%20And%20then%20I%20found%20it%20very%20fascinating%20how%20good%20it%20was%20to%20use%20local%20materials%20and%20artisans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20lies%20beneath%3A%20mining%20the%20truth%20about%20modern%20construction%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20down%20the%20line%2C%20practical%20stints%20with%20like-minded%20architects%20and%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20earthen%20materials%20cemented%20her%20resolve.%20But%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20charm%20of%20traditional%20methods%20that%20drew%20Krithika%20in.%20A%20hard-hitting%20look%20at%20the%20dark%20side%20of%20conventional%20construction%20materials%20truly%20solidified%20her%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20more%20important%20point%20for%20me%20to%20get%20into%20vernacular%20architecture%20was%20that%20we%20did%20a%20dissertation%20on%20construction%20materials%20and%20where%20they%20came%20from.%20So%2C%20I%20visited%20various%20mining%20sites%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krithika%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Krithika%20saw%20at%20those%20mining%20sites%20was%20a%20world%20apart%20from%20the%20glossy%20exteriors%20we%E2%80%99re%20used%20to%20admiring.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20look%20at%20sleek%20aluminium%20panels%20or%20polished%20granite%20floors%20and%20rarely%20stop%20to%20ask%20%E2%80%94%20where%20did%20this%20come%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBehind%20all%20that%20shine%20is%20a%20much%20darker%20story%20%E2%80%94%20environmental%20damage%2C%20materials%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20suit%20our%20climate%2C%20and%20scars%20left%20behind%20by%20mining.%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20a%20reality%20check%20that%20pushed%20her%20to%20rethink%20not%20just%20what%20we%20build%2C%20but%20how%20we%20build.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160418.061_11zon-1749206107.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22artisans%20doing%20their%20job%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160418.061_11zon-1749206107.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160418.061_11zon-1749206107-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160418.061_11zon-1749206107-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160418.061_11zon-1749206107-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160418.061_11zon-1749206107-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-445347%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20modern%20construction%20utilises%20less%20time%2C%20the%20health%20impact%20on%20the%20artisans%20were%20evident.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20waste%20and%20destruction%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20truly%20paying%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20the%20materials%20we%20were%20using.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20might%20buy%20a%20square%20foot%20of%20granite%20for%20Rs%20300%20%E2%80%94%20but%20think%20about%20the%20enormous%20amount%20of%20resources%20that%20go%20into%20extracting%20and%20producing%20that%20piece%20of%20stone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20on%20local%20communities%20was%20just%20as%20devastating%20%E2%80%94%20polluted%20water%2C%20ravaged%20landscapes%2C%20and%20disrupted%20lives.%20This%20eye-opening%20experience%20led%20to%20a%20fundamental%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CCan%20you%20build%20without%20using%20these%20materials%3F%20Or%20can%20you%20build%20without%20scraping%20out%20too%20many%20resources%20from%20the%20planet%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20concrete%20conundrum%3A%20beauty%20or%20beast%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Krithika%2C%20the%20answer%20was%20a%20resounding%20yes.%20And%20her%20gaze%20fell%20squarely%20on%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20culprits%20in%20mainstream%20construction%3A%20concrete.%20%E2%80%9CConcrete%20was%20not%20designed%20for%20residential%20structures%2C%20but%20for%20it%20to%20take%20up%20the%20mass%20vibration%20of%20industrial%20units%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mince%20her%20words%20about%20its%20environmental%20footprint.%20%E2%80%9CA%20single%20bag%20of%20cement%20