%20building%20practices%2C%20using%20materials%20that%20are%20kind%20to%20the%20earth%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20inhabit%20the%20structures.%20Her%20approach%20to%20building%20emphasises%20the%20use%20of%20natural%20and%20locally%20sourced%20materials%20and%20we%20have%20broken%20it%20down%20for%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20was%20such%20that%20not%20only%20did%20it%20give%20people%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F419684%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-using-stone-lime-moss-the-timber-residence-vagator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthier%20option%20to%20live%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20also%20the%20force%20that%20was%20working%20with%20these%20natural%20materials%20saw%20a%20betterment%20in%20their%20health.%20%E2%80%9CA%20few%20of%20my%20painters%20who%20do%20lime%20wash%20and%20lime%20plastic%20have%20told%20me%20that%20since%20they%20started%20working%20with%20natural%20substances%2C%20they%20did%20not%20encounter%20a%20problem%20of%20sinus%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhanajayan%20(52)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20mason%20since%20he%20was%2015%20years%20old%2C%20shares%20that%20he%20enjoys%20working%20for%20sustainable%20buildings.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20lime%20buildings%20since%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20involved%20in%20constructing%20buildings%20using%20traditional%20and%20old%20methods%20that%20eliminate%20concrete%20or%20cement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHappy%20clients%2C%20happy%20planet%3A%20A%20win-win%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWord%20of%20Krithika%E2%80%99s%20unique%20approach%20has%20spread%2C%20and%20her%20clients%20are%20enamoured%20with%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%9CSlowly%2C%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Krithika.%20They%20appreciate%20not%20just%20the%20aesth