s.%20That%E2%80%99s%20an%20important%20difference!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20might%20use%20the%20terms%20bi%2C%20bisexual%2C%20or%20bi%2B%20(which%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20more%20inclusive%20of%20identities%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354604%2Ftransgender-business-owners-pride-month-chandigarh-soul-spectrum-ishnoor-singh-dhananjay-chauhan-pride-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epansexual%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20queer%2C%20or%20fluid%20%E2%80%94%20all%20describing%20attraction%20to%20more%20than%20one%20gender).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20exploring%20this%20might%20also%20describe%20themselves%20as%20bicurious%2C%20meaning%20they%E2%80%99re%20still%20figuring%20out%20who%20they%E2%80%99re%20attracted%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESide%20note%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EBiphobia%20is%20the%20dislike%20of%20bisexual%20people.%20It%20often%20stems%20from%20harmful%20stereotypes%20like%20the%20false%20idea%20that%20bisexual%20people%20are%20unfaithful%2C%20promiscuous%2C%20or%20responsible%20for%20spreading%20sexually%20transmitted%20diseases%20(STDs).%20These%20beliefs%20are%20not%20only%20inaccurate%20but%20also%20deeply%20hurtful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-6-1749189799.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20can%20identify%20as%20transgender%20from%20the%20moment%20they%20realise%20their%20gender%20identity%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20match%20the%20label%20they%20were%20given%20at%20birth.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-6-1749189799.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-