%20(KVK)%2C%20he%20was%20giving%20a%20talk%20on%20modern%20farming%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20farmer%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrepreneur%20started%20with%20just%2021%20varieties%20of%20seeds%2C%20but%20now%20he%20grows%20over%2075%20varieties%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444412%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20started%20with%20just%2021%20varieties%20of%20seeds%2C%20but%20now%20he%20grows%20over%2075%20varieties%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20did%20not%20think%20of%20attending%20it%2C%20but%20what%20he%20said%20about%20using%20less%20space%20and%20water%20caught%20my%20attention.%20We%20were%20always%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20improve%20our%20yields%20with%20the%20limited%20land%20we%20had%2C%20and%20his%20techniques%20seemed%20like%20the%20solution%20we%20were%20searching%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20he%20has%20shifted%20to%20microgreens%20farming%2C%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20hard%20work%20and%20learning%20have%20seen%20a%20positive%20result.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20we%20could%20grow%206%2C500%20cauliflower%20bulbs%20in%205%20kanal%20of%20land.%20After%20learning%20from%20Mohit%2C%20we%20now%20produce%20over%2020%2C000%20bulbs%20in%20the%20same%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20proudly.%20The%20method%20also%20helped%20the%20farmer%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297512%2Findian-farmers-agroforestry-climate-change-solution-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20his%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMicrogreens%20farming%20allowed%20us%20to%20diversify%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20producing%20different%20seeds%20like%20cabbage%20and%20radish%20for%20Greenu%2C%20which%20has%20opened%20up%20a%20new%20stream%20of%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20training%20initiative%2C%20the%2046-year-old%20has%20taught%20over%20300%20farmers%20how%20to%20use%20minimal%20space%20to%20grow%20these%20high-value%20crops%2C%20helping%20them%20earn%20more%20with%20fewer%20resources.%20He%20also%20came%20across%20the%20incubation%20centre%20in%20Hisar%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20RKVY%20Raftaar%20scheme.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20business%20received%20support%20and%20funding%20through%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETiny%20greens%2C%20big%20impact%3A%20How%20Greenu%20expanded%20to%20growing%20over%2075%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Greenu%20entrepreneur%20believes%20that%20the%20beauty%20of%20microgreens%20farming%20lies%20in%20its%20simplicity%20and%20efficiency.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20venture%20by%20selecting%20high-quality%20and%20non%20genetically%20modified%20(non-GMO)%20seeds.%20I%20source%20mine%20from%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20(KVK)%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20organic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20seeds%20are%20sown%20in%20sterilised%20growing%20media%2C%20like%20cocopeat%20or%20coco%20coir%2C%20in%20trays.%20The%20microgreens%20are%20watered%20with%20a%20minimal%20amount%20of%20just%2030%20ml%20of%20water%20per%20tray%20daily.%20He%20does%20not%20use%20any%20chemicals%20or%20pesticides%20in%20his%20farming%20and%20only%20believes%20in%20following%20organic%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20a%20considerable%20investment%20of%20around%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20a%20small-scale%20microgreens%20operations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-768x402