C%20and%20is%20perfect%20for%20balconies%2C%20backyards%2C%20and%20beginner%20gardeners%20alike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%20City%20Running%20Out%20of%20Green%2C%20This%20Vast%20Vikhroli%20Mangrove%20Has%20Protected%20Mumbai%20for%204%20Decades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20driven%20from%20Mumbai%20towards%20Thane%20on%20the%20Eastern%20Express%20Highway%2C%20you%20might%20have%20felt%20a%20gradual%20dip%20in%20temperature%20of%20up%20to%20five%20degrees.%20As%20you%20pass%20Ghatkopar%20and%20approach%20Kanjurmarg%2C%20your%20windows%20fog%20up%20slightly%2C%20the%20air%20cools%2C%20and%20everything%20seems%20a%20little%20quieter.%20No%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20your%20imagination%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20mangroves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20your%20right%2C%20hidden%20behind%20the%20industrial%20facade%20of%20the%20city%2C%20lies%20one%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20best-kept%20secrets%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414695%2Fgorai-mangrove-park-in-mumbai-opening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esprawling%20mangrove%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20quietly%20flourishing%20within%20the%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pirojshanagar%20Township%20in%20Vikhroli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%20thousands%20of%20acres%2C%20this%20green%20lung%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20offering%20a%20cooler%20commute%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20regulating%20microclimates%2C%20filtering%20air%20and%20water%2C%20and%20shielding%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20shoreline%20from%20floods%20and%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%2C%20rainfall%20in%20this%20pocket%20is%20often%20heavier%20and%20gentler%2C%20absorbed%20by%20the%20thirsty%20roots%20of%20the%20mangroves.%20The%20Creekside%20Colony%2C%20one%20of%20three%20residential%20clusters%20near%20the%20forest%2C%20enjoys%20what%20residents%20call%20a%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20climate%E2%80%99%E2%80%94cleaner%20air%2C%20less%20heat%2C%20and%20an%20occasional%20chorus%20of%20birdsong.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20city%20constantly%20battling%20rising%20temperatures%2C%20waterlogging%2C%20and%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20just%20one%20visible%20outcome%20of%20a%20much%20deeper%2C%20long-term%20commitment.%20Since%20they%20acquired%20the%20land%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20has%20chosen%20to%20preserve%20and%20protect%20this%20mangrove%20ecosystem%2C%20not%20as%20a%20CSR%20project%2C%20not%20for%20branding%2C%20and%20not%20as%20a%20compliance%20tick%20box%E2%80%94but%20as%20an%20act%20of%20belief%E2%80%94a%20belief%20that%20business%20and%20biodiversity%20can%20exist%20harmoniously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20even%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20concrete%20jungle%2C%20a%20forest%20can%20be%20nurtured%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20care%20enough%20to%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20%E2%80%98wasteland%E2%80%99%20to%20ecological%20treasure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERewind%20to%20the%201940s%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time%20when%20mangroves%20were%20largely%20misunderstood.%20Often%20dismissed%20as%20marshy%20wastelands%20or%20potential%20real%20estate%2C%20they%20were%20left%20unprotected%2C%20encroached%20upon%2C%20and%20plundered%20for%20firewood%20by%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20late%20Sohrabji%20Godrej%2C%20a%20nature%20lover%20and%20industrialist%2C%20saw%20something%20others%20didn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ecosystem%20worth%20preserving.%20Under%20his%20guidance%2C%20Godrej%20initiated%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260147%2Finitiative-saving-mumbai-mangorves-environment-godrej-and-boyce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20scientific%20explorations%20in%20the%201980s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mangrove%20forest%20in%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444537%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGodrej%20delved%20into%20intense%20research%2C%20which%20laid%20the%20foundation%20to%20commence%20their%20conservation%20efforts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%2C%20led%20in%20consultation%20with%20none%20other%20than%20Dr%20Salim%20Ali%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20respected%20ornithologist%2C%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20conservation%20strategy%20that%20followed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20fence%20the%20forest%20and%20call%20it%20preservation.%20The%20early%20work%20involved%20a%20four-year%20baseline%20study%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doctorate-level%20research%20projects%20on%20mangrove%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tejashree%20Joshi%2C%20Head%20of%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20at%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20research%20uncovered%20not%20just%20which%20species%20lived%20here%2C%20but%20how%20they%20survived%2C%20coexisted%20or%20were%20at%20risk..%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%20when%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98mangrove%E2%80%99%20was%20confused%20with%20%E2%80%98mango%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20research%20provided%20the%20foundation%20and%20a%20science-backed%20roadmap%3A%20what%20to%20protect%2C%20where%20to%20intervene%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20why%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20an%20expert%20from%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20science%20rooted%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20data%20and%20information%2C%20the%20Godrej%20team%20rolled%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331813%2Fkochi-murukesan-plants-lakhs-of-mangrove-along-kerala-coastline-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree-pronged%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20model%20that%20still%20guides%20the%20initiative%20today%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Baseline%20biodiversity%20studies%2C%20continuous%20ecological%20monitoring%2C%20species%20inventory%20updates.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Securing%20the%20forest%2C%20replanting%20native%20mangroves%2C%20controlling%20access%2C%20and%20preventing%20exploitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20awareness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Educating%20employees%2C%20local%20communities%2C%20and%20schoolchildren%20through%20immersive%2C%20long-term%20engagement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20about%20ticking%20the%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Governance%20(ESG)%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20the%20work%20began%20decades%20before%20the%20term%20or%20even%20laws%20even%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20is%20not%20part%20of%20our%20CSR.%20It%E2%80%99s%20funded%20internally%20and%20has%20been%20since%20day%20one.%20That%20matters%2C%20because%20it%20reflects%20genuine%20belief%20rather%20than%20compliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20mangroves%20matter%20now%20more%20than%20ever%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20are%20often%20called%20the%20guardians%20of%20the%20coast%2C%20and%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20more%20truth%20than%20metaphor.%20These%20salt-tolerant%20forests%20act%20as%20natural%20infrastructure%2C%20quietly%20protecting%20the%20city%20from%20climate%20shocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMangroves%20trap%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20provide%20oxygen%2C%20protect%20against%20erosion%2C%20and%20serve%20as%20nurseries%20for%20aquatic%20life.%20In%20a%20coastal%20city%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20their%20value%20cannot%20be%20overstated%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dr.%20Ninad%2C%20the%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Natural%20climate%20defence%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20intensifying%20monsoons%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20flood%20risk%20grows%20each%20year.%20Mangroves%20act%20like%20sponges%2C%20absorbing%20excess%20rainwater%20and%20buffering%20coastlines%20from%20storm%20surges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%E2%80%99ve%20realised%20through%20research%20is%20that%20mangroves%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20stormwater%20drainage.%20When%20natural%20outlets%20are%20clogged%20or%20encroached%20upon%2C%20water%20can%E2%80%99t%20flow%20out%20into%20the%20sea%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20Mumbai%20floods.%20Mangroves%